S1:Disconectar cabo "vermelho" do switch,para desactivar internet

S2:Para cada computador, configurar a rede:
	->/etc/init.d/networking restart
	->ifconfig eth0 up

	Para Tux50:
	->ifconfig eth0 172.16.50.1  ----------pc4
	Para tux54:
	->ifconfig eth0 172.16.50.254 ----------- pc1
	


S3: --------PC1----------------------PC4------------
    --IP:172.16.50.1-------IP:172.16.50.254---------  
	 --MAC:00.0f.fe.8b.e4.a7--MAC:00:21:5a:c3:78:70--   
	 ------------------------------------------------

S4: ping IP

S5: route-n 

